messages.speech:
You'll set your password through Minnesota State's StarID Self Service when you activate your StarID.
https://starid.minnstate.edu/
Make sure you have one of the following available for reference:
Students
    Tech ID (Student ID)
    Library card barcode
    Personal email address (as listed in eServices)
    Verification code

Employees
    Tech ID (Employee ID)
    State Employee Number
    Library card barcode

Guests
    Personal email address
    Verification code
